title: The Shawshank Redemption - Stephen King [Audiobook]
description:
The Shawshank Redemption
                        - Audiobook -

When two giants team-up, power follows. King needs no introduction, and Library Journal calls Muller the first superstar of audio. In this program Muller tells King&#039;s earthy story of perseverance in Shawshank Prison in raw, gutteral tones. Harsh though the story is, the delivery carries the intimacy of a friend talking to the listener from the passenger seat. While the reading was so riveting I couldn&#039;t turn it off, there were times when it was so brutal I had to stop the tape. Muller&#039;s flawless reading enriches King&#039;s powerful story, providing a superlative audio program.
